    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies. This example delivers exceptional throttle response and linear power through its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is paired with a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. Critical maintenance is up to date, including documented rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul to ensure optimal variable valve timing. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative feedback and sharp turn-in synonymous with the M-chassis. While showing minor aesthetic wear consistent with its age, the car is structurally sound and performance-ready.",
      "price": 36500.0,
