      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm looking to find a new home for my car, and she\u2019s been such a reliable companion. It's in really solid shape and has been well-cared for over the years\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable ride without the 'brand new' price tag. It runs beautifully and is ready for many more road trips! Feel free to reach out if you want to come by, take a look, and go for a test drive. I'd love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have!",
